---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Page.astro";
import StepCard from "../../components/StepCard.astro";
---

<Layout
  content={{
    title: "Start Here",
    subtitle: "Your guide to joining the Syracuse tech community",
    hero: {
      imagePath: "/src/assets/clintonsquare.jpg",
      altText: "Historic photo of Clinton Square in Downtown Syracuse",
    },
  }}
>
  <p>
    Welcome! Whether you're new to Syracuse, new to tech, or just discovering our community,
    we're excited to have you. Here are the best ways to get involved:
  </p>

  <div class="not-prose">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <StepCard
        title="Join Our Slack Community"
        description="Connect with 700+ local developers in our active Slack workspace. Get help with code, share opportunities, and chat in channels like #general, #javascript, and #jobs."
        ctaText="Learn More"
        ctaHref="/start-here/slack"
        ctaExternal={false}
      />

      <StepCard
        title="Subscribe to Our Newsletter"
        description="Stay updated with monthly roundups of local tech events, job postings, and community highlights. Join 1,650+ subscribers!"
        ctaText="Learn More"
        ctaHref="/start-here/newsletter"
        ctaExternal={false}
      />

      <StepCard
        title="Attend a Meetup"
        description="Learn, network, and collaborate at recurring in-person events like OpenHack, Comp Sci Book Club, and general tech meetups. All skill levels welcome!"
        ctaText="Learn More"
        ctaHref="/start-here/meetups"
        ctaExternal={false}
      />

      <StepCard
        title="Browse Local Tech Jobs"
        description="Explore tech job opportunities from companies in Syracuse and Central New York. From startups to established firms, find your next role here."
        ctaText="Browse Jobs"
        ctaHref="/jobs"
        ctaExternal={false}
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>No Experience Required</h2>

  <p>
    Our community welcomes everyone regardless of experience level. Whether you're a beginner
    learning your first programming language or a senior engineer with decades of experience,
    you'll find supportive people who are excited to learn with you.
  </p>

  <h2>Code of Conduct</h2>

  <p>
    We're committed to maintaining a welcoming, inclusive community. Please review our
    <a href="/code-of-conduct">Code of Conduct</a> to understand our community standards.
  </p>
</Layout>
